{"title":"Elevate every ride with Castelli’s Espresso Collection","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/castelli-espresso-collection","date":1711722600000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/castelli-espresso-collection\">Elevate every ride with Castelli’s Espresso Collection</a></p>\n\n<p>Designed for every ride, the Espresso Collection is about to become your new favourite kit. Using Castelli’s latest technology, the Espresso Collection prioritises comfort without compromising on aerodynamics or fit. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Each piece not only looks good but is engineered to be fast and comfortable enough to be worn all day, every day.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Espresso Collection\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-2.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Castelli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The Espresso bib short features Espresso Doppio fabric which is soft, stretchy and gentle against the skin. Designed with an aerodynamic cut, the bib shorts are fast, allowing you to effectively cut through the air, and the raw-cut leg cuffs have silicone grippers which ensure everything stays in place. The bib shorts also have the Progetto X2 Air Seamless seat pad for all-day comfort on the saddle. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>What’s more, there is a colour for everyone as the men’s bib shorts come in eight colours and the women’s in six. </p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Espresso Collection\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-3.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Castelli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>Castelli also offers the Espresso short which has the same qualities as the bib short but is engineered specifically for those who prefer to ride without straps.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Espresso Collection\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-4.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Castelli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>A perfect pairing to the shorts is the Espresso jersey. Available in short and long sleeve, the jersey is made with Air_O Stretch fabric which boasts excellent breathability, sweat wicking properties and comfort. </p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-970x647.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Espresso Collection\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5-350x233.jpg 350w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-5.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Castelli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>The jersey has an aero fit without being too restrictive, allowing you to simply enjoy the ride. Choose from ten colourways for men, and eight for women.</p>\n\n\n<div>\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"546\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-970x546.jpg\" alt=\"Castelli Espresso Collection\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-970x546.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-300x169.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-768x432.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-750x422.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6-1140x641.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/03/castelli-espresso-collection-6.jpg 1200w\" /><figcaption>Castelli</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n<p>To complete the outfit is the Espresso 15 sock. It is made from Q Skin fibres which are antimicrobial and breathable, and features an extra footbed cushion for ultimate comfort on long rides. The socks come in four colours.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ride fast and ride comfortably with Castelli’s Espresso Collection – timeless kit made for every day.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>• <a href=\"https://espresso.castelli-cycling.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Discover the Castelli Espresso Collection</a></strong></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/sponsored/castelli-espresso-collection\">Elevate every ride with Castelli’s Espresso Collection</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Martin James","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"b7776db9335c2ebfec9a5b5274dce9a3f2b994e8241ffe0c21bffea189dd5b82","category":"Cycling"}